就平白让我受苦；<span class="_ _6"></span>我没有</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y131 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">做什么好事，<span class="_ _6"></span>他却让我天天快乐，<span class="_ _6"></span>这样的话，<span class="_ _6"></span>造物主可能会</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y132 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">常常被大家埋怨。 </div><div class="t m0 x1f h4 y113 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">其实，我们的人生之所以快乐，是由于过去做了善事；</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y107 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">之所以痛苦，是因为往昔造了恶业——这个概念乍听起来，</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y108 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">恐怕有些年轻人不接受，<span class="_ _5"></span>但它对每个人来讲至关重要。<span class="_ _5"></span>就好</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y10a ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">比你播下毒药的种子，<span class="_ _5"></span>结出来的果只能是毒药，<span class="_ _5"></span>绝不会是妙</div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
